{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Plan: 1. Add backend realtime delivery infrastructure: websocket endpoint, durable-event to realtime-event mapping, and composition chunk polling based on persisted job/segment state. 2. Extend composition runtime metadata and chunking s...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_88", "text": "Plan:\n1. Add backend realtime delivery infrastructure: websocket endpoint, durable-event to realtime-event mapping, and composition chunk polling based on persisted job/segment state.\n2. Extend composition runtime metadata and chunking so the worker persists reconnect-safe partial output and emits smaller, paced chunk checkpoints.\n3. Add frontend composition stream state and a real composition stage view that can render live chunks, recover from hydrated partial text, and expose composition controls.\n4. Add automated coverage for backend realtime behavior and frontend stream rendering, then run targeted tests, app build checks, and browser QA with screenshots.\n", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 175, "prompt_index": 63, "prompt_name": "62 \u2014 Composition Streaming Events", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T07:25:36-07:00"}
