{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented prompt 62 end to end. The backend now streams composition progress through the session realtime feed, emits `composition.chunk` plus durable `job.progress` and `job.status` events, and persists accepted manuscript/checkpoint...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_432", "text": "Implemented prompt 62 end to end. The backend now streams composition progress through the session realtime feed, emits `composition.chunk` plus durable `job.progress` and `job.status` events, and persists accepted manuscript/checkpoint metadata so reconnecting clients can recover safely. The frontend now has a dedicated composition stage with live manuscript rendering, progress and recap surfaces, composition controls, chat/action integration, and reconnect-aware runtime hydration.\n\nVerification completed:\n- Backend: targeted `pytest` coverage for websocket replay, chunk-delta synthesis, reconnect recovery, composition controls, redirect/rewrite flow, and chunk splitting/pacing.\n- Frontend: targeted Vitest coverage for the runtime store, realtime client, composition stage, action echoes, and workspace page.\n- Quality checks: `frontend` lint and build passed; touched backend files passed `ruff check`.\n- Browser QA: Docker Compose stack brought up, persisted DB migrated with `alembic upgrade head`, then live browser specs passed for both live chunk rendering and reconnect recovery. Screenshots were saved at [composition-live.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/composition-live.png) and [composition-reconnect.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/composition-reconnect.png).\n\nI made three commits on the current branch:\n- `bcced2e` `feat(prompt-62): stream composition events from backend`\n- `5bf4792` `feat(prompt-62): render live composition chunks in workspace`\n- `c9ebf5d` `test(prompt-62): verify streaming chunk pacing`\n\nThe required reviewer summary was written as the final repo change at [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/62_composition_streaming_events/summary.md).", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 885, "prompt_index": 63, "prompt_name": "62 \u2014 Composition Streaming Events", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T08:15:23-07:00"}
